OL,6,FHis fingerprints were later found on
OL,7,Fthe bodywork, Sheffield Magistrates'
OL,8,FCourt heard on Thursday.
OL,10,FProsecutor Simon Walton said the
OL,11,Fpolice community support officer
OL,12,Finside the vehicle "described fearing
OL,13,Ffor his life".
OL,15,FThe officer got into the driver's seat
OL,16,Fand managed to drive it away.
OL,18,FRoughley yawned in the glass-fronted
OL,19,Fdock as he confirmed his details and
OL,20,Fpleaded guilty to one count of violent
OL,21,Fdisorder.
