OL,6,FThe court heard how despite only
OL,7,Frecently turning 18, the defendant has
OL,8,Fprevious convictions for assaulting an
OL,9,Femergency worker and racially
OL,10,Faggravated harassment.
OL,12,FHe is still under youth justice
OL,13,Fsupervision following the latter
OL,14,Foffence, the court heard.
OL,16,FDistrict Judge James Gould refused
OL,17,FRoughley bail and remanded him in
OL,18,Fcustody to appear at Sheffield Crown
OL,19,FCourt on Friday.
