OL,6,FRoughley was one of four people who
OL,7,Fappeared at the court in Sheffield on
OL,8,FThursday morning in connection with
OL,9,Fthe Rotherham incident, which saw
OL,10,Frioters enter the hotel through a
OL,11,Fsmashed-in fire door and try to set it
OL,12,Falight using a burning bin.
OL,14,FOver the course of this week, the
OL,15,Fcourt has heard how police estimated
OL,16,F500 people attended at the hotel, with
OL,17,Faround 100 actively taking part in the
OL,18,Fviolence.
