OL,3,CTeen admits part in rocking police van
OL,4,Cduring Rotherham riot
OL,6,FLevi Fishlock, 31, is accused of being
OL,7,Fpart of a group which pushed the
OL,8,Fburning bin against the hotel after
OL,9,Fdropping wood into the fire.
OL,11,FFishlock, of Sheffield Road, Barnsley,
OL,12,Fdenied violent disorder and arson with
OL,13,Fintent to endanger life when he
OL,14,Fappeared on Thursday.
OL,16,FJudge Gould heard how he is also
OL,17,Faccused of throwing missiles at police.
OL,19,FFishlock was remanded in custody and
OL,20,Fwill next appear at Sheffield Crown
OL,21,FCourt on 20 August 20.
