OL,6,FAlfie Conway, 19, of Park Avenue,
OL,7,FPontefract, denied violent disorder
OL,8,Fand was also remanded in custody to
OL,9,Fappear at Sheffield Crown Court on the
OL,10,Fsame date.
OL,12,FA 16-year-old boy admitted violent
OL,13,Fdisorder and was initially given bail
OL,14,Fbefore a sentencing hearing at
OL,15,FBarnsley Youth Court on 20 August, but
OL,16,Fhe was then remanded in custody after
OL,17,Fthe Crown Prosecution Service said it
OL,18,Fwould appeal against the judge's
OL,19,Fdecision to grant bail.
